All actions are straight forward and simple to use. Simply use a black or white brush to increase or decrease action effects.

Included Actions:
JRP Workflow:
Warmer
Cooler
Yellow Remover
Red Remover
Brighten
Pop

Haze
Sharpen
Web Resize

I personally created this action based off my every day workflow :)

name: Hand spun Merino yarn by the oz.
description:
Want to create your own goodies? JPC is now offering hand spun merino yarn. You pick the color and well spin you a sweet soft merino yarn. Yarn size will have a nice variation. Average yardage per ounce is approx 35-45 yards.

purchasing in bulk? order 50 oz or more of merino yarn ( mix and match colors.. and get 10% off you order with code YARN10

order 100 oz or more and get 20 % off your order with code YARN20.




please allow up to 2 weeks for your yarn to be spun and shipped. some colors may need to be ordered before your yarn is created. 

* Listing is for 1 ounce of spun fiber. please add the desired amount of fiber you would like spun by changing the quantity :)


(no rush orders allowed for hand spun yarn)


**Last image is to show a newborn bonnet created with our hand spun merino yarn.
